<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="428" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,151,968]" pageId="27" pageNumber="428">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,316,871,896]" pageId="27" pageNumber="428">Variation.</emphasis>
Body smaller; head slightly wider than long; cuspis with ventral arm narrower basally and apex of dorsal arm somewhat blunt; but the most prominent variation is the 
<typeStatus box="[910,1006,909,933]" pageId="27" pageNumber="428">paratype</typeStatus>
has the metapectal-propodeal disc not strongly areolate nor posteriorly substriate.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
